edu.byu.cs.tweeter.model.service.request

Class FollowingRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.byu.cs.tweeter.model.service.request.GetFollowingRequest

  • public class FollowingRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains all the information needed to make a request to have the server return the next page of followees for a specified follower.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      User getFollower()
      Returns the follower whose followees are to be returned by this request.
      User getLastFollowee()
      Returns the last followee that was returned in the previous request or null if there was no previous request or if no followees were returned in the previous request.
      int getLimit()
      Returns the number representing the maximum number of followees to be returned by this request.
